785
01:01:09,625 --> 01:01:11,085
Yes

786
01:01:13,296 --> 01:01:14,964
This belongs to Jesus Christ Inc

787
01:01:15,131 --> 01:01:17,133
- Are they still in business?
- Yes.

788
01:01:18,718 --> 01:01:20,345
Are they still in business?

789
